data.title: SEA FURY: (AIRCRAFT) RECOGNITION SHORT NO 3 [Main Title]
data.meta_description: Aircraft recognition film featuring the Hawker Sea Fury. General views of the Sea Fury are followed by a sequence in which the aircraft is halted in flight in different aspects while the commentary draws attention to the recognition points. The aircraft is then shown landing, on the ground and taking off.

We have over a million object records online, and we are adding to this all the time. Our records are never finished.
